                <p dir=3D"ltr" style=3D"text-align: justify;"><b><strong>Ad=
jacency Matrix</strong></b><span> is a square matrix used to represent a fi=
nite graph. The elements of the matrix indicate whether pairs of vertices a=
re adjacent or not in the graph. An adjacency matrix is a simple and straig=
htforward way to represent graphs and is particularly useful for dense grap=
hs.</span></p><div id=3D"table_of_content"><p style=3D"margin:4px; font-siz=
e:20px; font-weight:bold;">Table of Content</p><ul><li><a href=3D"https://w=
