trix for Undirected and Weighted graph:</a></li><li><a href=3D"https://www.=
geeksforgeeks.org/dsa/adjacency-matrix/#3-adjacency-matrix-for-directed-and=
-unweighted-graph">3. Adjacency Matrix for Directed and Unweighted graph:</=
a></li><li><a href=3D"https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/dsa/adjacency-matrix/#4=
